org.jtimer.Annotations.Handler

Class AnnotationHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jtimer.Annotations.Handler.AnnotationHandler

  • public class AnnotationHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    An object that is able to handle all meta annotations of a AnnotatedElement object. If annotations are repeated, then only the topmost annotation present will be the one returned, if it's needed.
    Author:
    MagneticZero
